title: Airline, Airport, Traveler and Tourism Groups Urge Congress to Ground Revenue Diversion Plan
text: WASHINGTON--(BUSINESS WIRE)--A coalition of travel, tourism, airport and airline groups are urging leaders to not divert $9.2 billion collected for aviation security, to pay for the highway trust fund ...
